;est pas facile.</p></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-vibrant rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div><p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">Les patients ont des besoins en matière de soins de santé qui s&#x27;étendent bien au-delà d&#x27;une visite à la clinique ou à l&#x27;hôpital.</p></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-vibrant rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div><p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">L&#x27;expertise médicale requise n&#x27;est pas toujours disponible localement</p></div><div class="flex items-start gap-4"><div class="w-3 h-3 bg-blue-vibrant rounded-full flex-shrink-0 mt-2"></div><p class="text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">De plus, le nombre croissant de patients atteints de maladies chroniques oblige les médecins à établir des moyens efficaces, pratiques et réactifs de soutenir les patients chroniques.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16 bg-gray-50"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8"><div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="relative lg:order-1"><img alt="Patient utilisant la technologie de santé" loading="lazy" width="640" height="500" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" class="rounded-2xl shadow-2xl w-full h-auto max-h-[500px] object-cover" style="color:transparent" srcSet="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.pexels.com%2Fphotos%2F4386467%2Fpexels-photo-4386467.jpeg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26cs%3Dtinysrgb%26w%3D1260%26h%3D750%26dpr%3D2&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.pexels.com%2Fphotos%2F4386467%2Fpexels-photo-4386467.jpeg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26cs%3Dtinysrgb%26w%3D1260%26h%3D750%26dpr%3D2&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 2x" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.pexels.com%2Fphotos%2F4386467%2Fpexels-photo-4386467.jpeg%3Fauto%3Dcompress%26cs%3Dtinysrgb%26w%3D1260%26h%3D750%26dpr%3D2&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75"/></div><div class